# Commit Structure:
#
# [commit type]: [title] (#[issue-number])
#
# - Brief description of the commit purpose and changes.
#
####################################################################
#
# Title Rules:
# - Use a summary in the imperative mood.
# - Keep the title to no more than 50 characters.
#
# Commit Types:
#
# feat:     A new feature
# fix:      A bug fix
# docs:     Documentation changes
# style:    Code style changes (formatting, white-space, etc.)
# refactor: Code refactoring without adding features or fixing bugs
# test:     Adding or correcting tests
# chore:    Maintenance tasks (build process, dependencies, etc.)
